    <!--
        These color palettes follow the design team's spec:
        https://www.figma.com/file/ZJfEMS2fVY0TdB2Ao3uWv8/FINAL-Pocket-Design-System?node-id=3434%3A3542

        All colors should be defined in this file and should use the official palette.
        Do not define color outside of this file.

        If a new color is introduced that doesn't match the palette, double check
        with design that they intended to introduce a new color. If it is a new color,
        ask for a name, and a dark color to go with it.

        For most components, when you reference a color, you can use the pkt_themed_*  version to
        automatically get dark mode support for your component. However, at times, for
        certain components there may be exceptions to those rules. If there is an exception to the
        default color pairings, please add a comment with `theme-pairing-exception` in your state
        list file to make it obvious that it was intentional.
    -->

